*Razmišljaš* li o tome? (Are you thinking about it?)
Šta *razmišljaš*? (What are you thinking?) 
Šta god da *razmišljaš*, recite mi. (Whatever you're thinking, tell me.) 
On je znao šta *razmišlja*. (He knew what he was thinking.) 
Ona je uvek *razmišljala* o budućnosti. (She was always thinking about the future.)